2. cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is also likely as the paper includes experiments on image captioning. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper proposes a novel model for improving the performance of self-attention based Transformer. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper proposes a new method for improving attention mechanisms in deep learning models. 
5. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is also a possible category as the paper proposes a new method for improving the performance of neural networks.
